1
00:01:43,727 --> 00:01:45,996
<i>Her name is Mikuru Asahina.</i>

2
00:01:46,554 --> 00:01:49,969
<i>On the outside, she seems like a
normal, kind, and extremely cute girl.</i>

3
00:01:50,297 --> 00:01:53,196
<i>But in reality, she's a battle waitress from the future.</i>

4
00:01:53,671 --> 00:01:58,423
<i>Don't ask me why she's from the future or why
she's a waitress 'cause that's not important right now.</i>

5
00:01:58,751 --> 00:02:01,726
<i>It's just a couple of minor details
you need to have shoved down your throat,</i>

6
00:02:01,751 --> 00:02:03,899
<i>before this particular story can kick into gear.</i>

7
00:02:05,019 --> 00:02:12,268
Um... Not to bother you people or anything. We got a
lotta good, crispy nappa cabbage in the store today.

8
00:02:12,293 --> 00:02:15,501
Uh... Did I mention that for the next hour only,

9
00:02:15,793 --> 00:02:18,816
all nappa cabbage is on sale for half price!

10
00:02:19,719 --> 00:02:22,684
<i>By the way, earlier I mentioned she was a battle waitress,</i>

11
00:02:22,757 --> 00:02:26,051
<i>so you're probably wondering why
she's wearing a bunny girl costume here.</i>

12
00:02:26,478 --> 00:02:27,935
<i>You see, that's because during the day,</i>

13
00:02:27,960 --> 00:02:31,966
<i>she has a part-time job attracting customers
