Hi, Mikuru! Looks like you're workin' hard out here today.

18
00:02:46,157 --> 00:02:48,148
Why, yes! I'm trying my best!

19
00:02:48,272 --> 00:02:49,864
<i>Mikuru answers cheerfully,</i>

20
00:02:49,915 --> 00:02:52,215
<i>in an outfit that screams "trying too hard."</i>

21
00:02:52,455 --> 00:02:56,588
<i>And so, thanks to her innocent charm,
the nappa cabbage sold out in record time.</i>

22
