28
00:03:22,207 --> 00:03:25,343
Accuse me... Ah! Excuse me.

29
00:03:28,063 --> 00:03:31,089
<i>The girl had become a sort of
mascot for the local retailers.</i>

30
00:03:31,251 --> 00:03:34,423
<i>And she was loved by all the
people who lived in the neighborhood.</i>

31
00:03:35,102 --> 00:03:36,560
<i>You can do it, Mikuru!</i>

32
00:03:36,683 --> 00:03:41,113
<i>Bring back the customers who flock like lemmings to
that huge mega-warehouse store that opened last year.</i>

33
00:03:41,811 --> 00:03:46,077
<i>The fate of this neighborhood and its mom and
pop stores is riding on your shoulders, Mikuru.</i>

34
00:03:47,198 --> 00:03:50,615
<i>Unfortunately, none of this
has anything to do with the story.</i>

35
00:03:55,210 --> 00:03:57,244
<i>Anyway, getting back to the story,</i>

36
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:59,619
<i>she's actually a battle waitress.</i>

37
00:03:59,883 --> 00:04:04,374
