120
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:51,701
That's all I am. Well, goodbye!

121
00:09:58,666 --> 00:10:00,418
Just who in the world, is she?

122
00:10:01,139 --> 00:10:02,955
<i>With a forced look of awe on his face,</i>

